lead_paragraph: England striker Wayne Rooney says it is highly unlikely that a scenario would arise causing him to switch allegiances to any Premier League side other than Manchester United or boyhood club Everton in the future.

headline.print_headline: Rooney Rules Out Future Move to New Premier League Club
headline.main: Rooney Rules Out Future Move to New Premier League Club
